main event: A teacher reported a UFO sighting with related photographs taken while parked at Wreck Pond in Spring Lake, New Jersey on February 20, 1965.
interesting points: The investigation is part of Project Blue Book, an Air Force program to investigate UFOs., The reports indicate that numerous photographs were taken of the unidentified object., The UFO was visible to the naked eye., The correspondent expressed hope that the investigations would focus on the sightings themselves rather than just the photographs., Air Force Intelligence stated that they could not analyze the submitted photographs due to a lack of negatives.
witness description: a teacher who took photographs from their automobile
